question: Sankalp Se Siddhi Program was launched in ___________.
explanation: Prime Minister Narendra Modi launched New India movement from 2017-2022, a Sankalp Se Siddhi (Attainment through Resolve) Program was organized at Coimbatore. It organized an India free of Poverty, Corruption, Terrorism, Communalism, Casteism, and Un-cleanliness.
